Localization.Name: Battle of Vega II Vanduul Skull
Localization.Description: Featuring a preserved skull from a defeated Vanduul footsoldier, this special commemorative display honors the brave members of the UEE military and public who fought so valiantly at the Battle of Vega II on October 5th, 2945.
